    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just that i've changed. it feels more permanent than that. like the person who actually had dreams and a soul is just... gone. and what's left is just this exhausting, empty routine. it feels like i'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore. like i'm just waiting for something to happen that never will.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
